    "Name": "Fer-de-Lance FDL-4",
    "Details": "Created during the heyday of the Star League era, the Fer-de-Lance is a 30 ton Cannopian BattleMech built by Majesty Metals and Manufacturing at their Canopus IV facilities. Surviving the succession wars mostly intact, the Fer-de-Lance is still produced in small quantities by MMM every year and features in most MAF light mech lances. The FDL-4 is built around a 240 rated XL engine. Outfitted to hunt enemy scout units, the FDL-4 boasts a pair of clan made Improved Heavy Medium Lasers and a pair of Medium Pulse Lasers. Angel ECM and Stealth armor round out the design.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Nimble</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 0.99</color></b>",
    "Icon": "uixTxrIcon_spider"
